title: Alan Moore's DC Universe
description:
Well, this is my first up here at PB. It includes most of Alan Moore's work on DC aside form The Killing Joke, Swamp Thing, Watchmen(and maybe something else, I'm not sure). Here's the contents list:

- Secret Origins # 10 (Phantom Stranger's multiple origins)

- Omega Men (all Alan Moore's)

- Batman Annual # 11 (an excellent story featuring Clayface III)

- All Alan Moore's Green Lantern (includes "In Blackest Night", "Mogo doesn't socialize", and "Tygers")

-Superman Annual #11 (For The Man Who Has Everything)

- Green Arrow_Night Olympics (Detective 549-550)

- Superman- Whatever Happened to the Man of Tomorrow

- Vigilante #17-18: Father's Day

- Superman and Swamp Thing: The Jungle Line.

Not my scans. I thank to the original scanners (whomever they be, these scans aren't signed)

Upped in attending of hyatmarc's request on the Alan Moore Collection's torrent.

I'll be upping some other Alan Moore obscure material some time soon.
